	•	Blob lifecycle: delete previous versions > N days (e.g., 30).
	•	Poison handling: if a doc keeps failing, log to a “dead‑letter” container with the docId + exception.
	•	Backpressure: Service Bus Auto‑scale or use Topic + multiple subscribers if throughput grows.

