10) Testing checklist
	•	CREATE with no rule satisfied → no notify, baseline created.
	•	CREATE with rule satisfied → notify once, baseline created.
	•	MODIFY touching non‑rule fields → no notify, mirror overwritten.
	•	MODIFY touching rule fields but rule false → no notify, mirror overwritten.
	•	MODIFY touching rule fields and rule true → notify once, mirror overwritten.
	•	Concurrency: simulate 2 function instances writing the same mirror → one succeeds, other gets 412, retries after reload.

